Library
    Default-Language: Haskell2010
    Ghc-Options:     -O2
    Hs-Source-Dirs:  src
    Exposed-Modules: Data.ByteString.Lex.Integral
                     Data.ByteString.Lex.Fractional
    Other-Modules:   Data.ByteString.Lex.Internal

